text:
Worst dining experience ever.
We booked a table during valentine day, just a few table when we arrived, food took us 40mins - 1 hour to arrive not sure what’s the issue. We didn’t finish the food and left because feel really unpleasant with the services…
I just love this place. Went there twice while staying on Sentosa Island. The food is delicious, reasonably priced and the staff is amazingly friendly. Cannot recommend Yue Bar more.

No wonder is empty , drinks take about 30 min to arrive , I ordered fries and took them 1h 20 min to come …. Also I did need to look for them several times to pay my bill and leave . As there is no staff in the bar .
The boss is very nice, the service attitude is also very good, and the food is delicious!
